      "Spellcasting": {
        "description": "You get spellcasting abilities at level 1. Your spellcasting ability is Wisdom, so your spell save DC = 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Wisdom modifier and your spell attack modifier = your proficiency bonus + your Wisdom modifier. You can prepare a number of spells equal to your cleric level plus your Wisdom modifier. You can also cast spells that you have prepared as rituals if it has the ritual tag."
